      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4 class="panel-title">
        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThirtyThree">
          Cost
        </a>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="collapseThirtyThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <p>$0.00. Feel free to donate/gift items <%=link_to "here", "http://steamcommunity.com/profiles/76561198079056731/"%>, and if you haven’t already, purchase the <%=link_to "AD2L Season 3 Open ticket", "http://www.dota2.com/store/itemdetails/15548?r=1f4"%> and/or the <%=link_to "AD2L Season 3 invitational ticket", "http://www.dota2.com/store/itemdetails/20428?r=ce/"%> which includes a courier!.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4 class="panel-title">
        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThirtyFour">
          Format
        </a>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="collapseThirtyFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <ol>
          <li>1. Best of One, Single Elimination, semi-finals and finals will be Best of 3</li>
          <li>2. All games will be played on default server EU WEST( EU tournament)  US EAST(US tournament), unless both players agree on another server </li>
          <li>3. Only Middle mode - hero will be decided in the lobby.</li>
          <li>4. Heroes can be voted on <%= link_to "here", "http://strawpoll.me/1688881", :target => "blank"%>.</li>
        <ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="panel panel-default">
    <div class="panel-heading">
      <h4 class="panel-title">
        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThirtyFive">
          Rules
        </a>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="collapseThirtyFive" class="panel-collapse collapse">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <ol>
          <li>1. No team is allowed to be more than 15 minutes late.</li>
          <li>2. When both players are in the lobby there will be 3 minutes to decide on what hero will be played. If a decision has not been made by the 3 minutes the admin will choose the hero (the admin can allow the caster to pick the hero if the lobby has one.).</li>
        <ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
