          <li>3. Add <%=link_to "Affinity", "players/140"%> on Steam</li>
          <li>3. Add <%=link_to "Boycey", "players/1615"%> on Steam</li>
          <li>3. Add <%=link_to "Trenza", "players/4745"%> on Steam</li>
